member.summary: This enum is used to classify the user agent device into some common categorie.

member.name: F:OrbintSoft.Yauaa.Classify.DeviceClass.Desktop
member.summary: The device is assessed as a Desktop/Laptop class device.

member.name: F:OrbintSoft.Yauaa.Classify.DeviceClass.Anonymized
member.summary: In some cases the useragent has been altered by anonimization software.

member.name: F:OrbintSoft.Yauaa.Classify.DeviceClass.Mobile
member.summary: A device that is mobile yet we do not know if it is a eReader/Tablet/Phone or Watch.

member.name: F:OrbintSoft.Yauaa.Classify.DeviceClass.Tablet
member.summary: A mobile device with a rather large screen (common > 7").

member.name: F:OrbintSoft.Yauaa.Classify.DeviceClass.Phone
member.summary: A mobile device with a small screen (common < 7").

member.name: F:OrbintSoft.Yauaa.Classify.DeviceClass.Watch
member.summary: A mobile device with a tiny screen (common < 2"). Normally these are an additional screen for a phone/tablet type device.

member.name: F:OrbintSoft.Yauaa.Classify.DeviceClass.VirtualReality
member.summary: A mobile device with a VR capabilities.

member.name: F:OrbintSoft.Yauaa.Classify.DeviceClass.EReader
member.summary: Similar to a Tablet yet in most cases with an eInk screen.

member.name: F:OrbintSoft.Yauaa.Classify.DeviceClass.SetTopBox
member.summary: A connected device that allows interacting via a TV sized screen.

member.name: F:OrbintSoft.Yauaa.Classify.DeviceClass.TV
member.summary: Similar to Set-top box yet here this is built into the TV.

member.name: F:OrbintSoft.Yauaa.Classify.DeviceClass.GameConsole
member.summary: 'Fixed' game systems like the PlayStation and XBox.

member.name: F:OrbintSoft.Yauaa.Classify.DeviceClass.HandheldGameConsole
member.summary: 'Mobile' game systems like the 3DS.

member.name: F:OrbintSoft.Yauaa.Classify.DeviceClass.Robot
member.summary: Robots that visit the site.

member.name: F:OrbintSoft.Yauaa.Classify.DeviceClass.RobotMobile
member.summary: Robots that visit the site indicating they want to be seen as a Mobile visitor.

member.name: F:OrbintSoft.Yauaa.Classify.DeviceClass.RobotImitator
member.summary: Robots that visit the site pretending they are robots like google, but they are not.

member.name: F:OrbintSoft.Yauaa.Classify.DeviceClass.Hacker
member.summary: In case scripting is detected in the useragent string, also fallback in really broken situations.

member.name: F:OrbintSoft.Yauaa.Classify.DeviceClass.Unknown
member.summary: We really don't know, these are usually useragents that look normal yet contain almost no information about the device.

member.name: F:OrbintSoft.Yauaa.Classify.DeviceClass.Unclassified
member.summary: We found a deviceclass string that we have no enum value for.
